description.en: ARCEE COIN is accessible and available wherever and whenever you are in need, no limits, no bounderires, which means you can purchase or sell products and services, transfer money to your family and friends at an extremely low cost by an instant conﬁrmation network without any interruption. We also provide you with our debit card system, which can be easily used via your smart phone.
